1980: 22% * Spain: 1995 (forecast): 66% 1980: 18% * France: 1995 (forecast): 
66% 1980: 37% * Germany: 1995 (forecast): 60% 1980: 33% * Britain: 1995 
(forecast): 56% 1980: 54% * UNITED STATES: 1995 (forecast): 64% 1980: 38% * 
