<P>
Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA021594-0094 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 013603 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 15, 1994, Tuesday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 2; Metro Desk 
