la Louisa in Laguna Hills, (714) 678-7771. 
</P>
<P>
 * Saturday and Feb. 26; 9 a.m. to 1 p.m., Laguna Beach Senior Center in Lang 
Park, 384 Legion St., (714) 497-2441. 
</P>
<P>
 * Feb. 28 and March 1; 8 a.m. to noon, Norman P. Murray Community and Senior 
Center, 24932 Oso Viejo in Mission Viejo, (714) 348-2063. 
