VENTURA COUNTY REVIEW / JACK SEARLES: ACCESS HEALTHNET TO SUPPLY 20 HOSPITALS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Jack Searles 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Access Healthnet Inc., a Westlake Village provider of communications systems 
that connect doctors, hospitals and laboratories, has signed a deal to supply 
its networks to Community Health Systems Inc., a Brentwood, Tenn., company that 
operates 20 hospitals in the South, Midwest and West. 
</P>
